en_319012_0	All Officers and Other Rankers of the 66 Division under the Security Force Headquarters - Kilinochchi (SFHQ-KLN) co-sponsored the distribution of a stock of school accessories among students of low-income families in Bogaswewa, Vavuniya on Tuesday (12).
en_319012_1	Six clever students of Bogaswewa Maha Vidyalaya were the beneficiaries of the arrangement after troops with the support of school authorities selected those students considering their economic plight and hardships.
en_319012_2	Officers and Other Rankers voluntarily co-sponsored the purchase of those items for students after the realities were brought to the notice of those soldiers.
en_319012_3	Some of those troops have served Bogaswewa area before they moved to 66 Division in Pooneryn.
en_319012_4	Brigadier Deepthi Jayathilaka, General Officer Commanding, 66 Division attended the occasion at the 66 Division premises as the Chief Guest.
en_319012_5	Senior Officers, parents and teachers were among the gathering.
